{
  "template": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"de-de\" xmlns:th=\"http://www.thymeleaf.org\">\n\n<head>\n  <meta charset=\"utf-8\">\n  <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\">\n  <meta name=\"description\" content=\"\">\n  <meta name=\"author\" content=\"\">\n  <meta name=\"robots\" content=\"\">\n  <meta property=\"og:url\" content=\"\">\n  <meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"\">\n  <meta property=\"og:description\" content=\"\">\n  <meta property=\"og:image\" content=\"\">\n  <link rel=\"icon\" href=\"_res/favicon.ico\">\n\n  <link rel=\"preload\" href=\"_res/fonts/boschsans/BoschSans-Regular.woff2\" as=\"font\" type=\"font/woff2\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\">\n  <link rel=\"preload\" href=\"_res/fonts/boschsans/BoschSans-Black.woff2\" as=\"font\" type=\"font/woff2\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\">\n  <link rel=\"preload\" href=\"_res/fonts/boschsans/BoschSans-Medium.woff2\" as=\"font\" type=\"font/woff2\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\">\n  <link rel=\"preload\" href=\"_res/fonts/boschsans/BoschSans-Bold.woff2\" as=\"font\" type=\"font/woff2\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\">\n  <link rel=\"preload\" href=\"_res/fonts/boschsans/BoschSans-Light.woff2\" as=\"font\" type=\"font/woff2\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\">\n  <link rel=\"preload\" href=\"_res/icons/bosch-pt-icons.woff2\" as=\"font\" type=\"font/woff2\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\">\n\n  <link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" href=\"_res/critical.css\">\n\n  <link rel=\"preload\" href=\"_res/main.css\" as=\"style\" onload=\"this.onload=null;this.rel='stylesheet'\">\n  <noscript><link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"_res/main.css\"></noscript>\n\n  <title> | Bosch PT Frontend</title>\n\n  <style>\n    .ComponentViewHeader {\n      padding: 8px;\n      overflow-x: auto;\n    }\n\n    @media (min-width: 768px) {\n      .ComponentViewHeader {\n        display: flex;\n      }\n    }\n\n    .ComponentView {\n      position: relative;\n      border-top: 8px solid var(--bosch-gray-80);\n      border-bottom: 8px solid var(--bosch-gray-80);\n      background-image:\n              linear-gradient(45deg, var(--bosch-gray-90) 25%, transparent 25%),\n              linear-gradient(-45deg, var(--bosch-gray-90) 25%, transparent 25%),\n              linear-gradient(45deg, transparent 75%, var(--bosch-gray-90) 75%),\n              linear-gradient(-45deg, transparent 75%, var(--bosch-gray-90) 75%);\n      background-size: 16px 16px;\n      background-position: 0 0, 0 8px, 8px calc(-1 * 8px), calc(-1 * 8px) 0;\n    }\n\n    .ComponentViewOptions {\n      display: flex;\n      margin-left: auto;\n      align-items: center;\n    }\n\n    .ComponentViewCta {\n      padding: 0 4px;\n    }\n\n    .ComponentViewCta a {\n      display: block;\n    }\n\n    .ComponentViewCta .Icon {\n      width: 32px;\n      height: 32px;\n    }\n\n    .ComponentViewHeader .Theme-selector {\n      padding: 4px;\n    }\n\n    .ComponentViewHeader .list-inline {\n      display: inline;\n      list-style: none;\n      padding: 0;\n    }\n\n    .ComponentViewHeader .list-inline>li {\n      display: inline;\n    }\n\n    .ComponentViewHeader .list-middot>li:not(:last-child)::after {\n      content: \"\\00b7\";\n    }\n\n    .ComponentViewHeader .list-pipe>li:not(:last-child)::after {\n      content: \"|\";\n      margin: 0 .25em;\n    }\n  </style>\n</head>\n\n<body dir=\"ltr\">\n<!-- This layout (Components.njk) is only used during component development -->\n\n<!-- Component Info Header -->\n<header class=\"ComponentViewHeader\">\n  <div>\n    <div><strong>Name:</strong> gt/o/o200-gt-stage/o200-gt-stage.njk</div>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"ComponentViewOptions\">\n    <!--<div class=\"ComponentViewCta\">\n      <select class=\"Theme-selector\">\n        <option value=\"Theme-light Section-bgWhite\" selected>Light</option>\n        <option value=\"Theme-dark Section-bgBlue\">Dark</option>\n      </select>\n    </div>-->\n    <div class=\"ComponentViewCta\">\n      <a href=\"_res/icons/demo.html\">\n        <i class=\"icon-jewel\"></i>\n      </a>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"ComponentViewCta\">\n      <a href=\"./\">\n        <i class=\"icon-Bosch-Ic-wishlist-black\"></i>\n      </a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</header>\n\n  <div class=\"ComponentView\">\n    <!-- BEGIN: Component Markup -->\n\n    <section class=\"o-gt-stage\" th:classappend=\"|trackingModule sm-pt-20|\" th:fragment=\"o_gt_stage\">\n      <div class=\"m-gt-grid\">\n        <a href=\"#\" class=\"back-link link backlink\" th:remove=\"all\">\n          <span>Test Result</span>\n          <i class=\"icon-Bosch-Ic-black\"></i>\n        </a>\n\n        <div class=\"o-gt-stage__labels\" th:if=\"${#bools.isTrue($skuAttr(NOVELTY)$.getBoolVal())}\">\n          <div class=\"o-gt-stage__label\" th:if=\"${#bools.isTrue($skuAttr(NOVELTY)$.getBoolVal())}\">\n            <span th:text=\"§t-productlistingpage.new§\">New</span>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"m-gt-grid__container-fluid\">\n          <div class=\"m-gt-grid__col col-12\">\n            <div class=\"o-gt-stage__flag\"><div class=\"flag flag--expert\">expert</div></div>\n            <div class=\"o-gt-stage__wrapper\">\n              <div class=\"o-gt-stage__intro\">\n                <h1 class=\"bba bba--hl4\" $skuAttr(TITLE)$.getText()>EXSR 18V-150</h1>\n                <h2 class=\"bba bba--medium\" $skuAttr(PRODUCTDESCRIPTION)$.getText()>Akku-Bohrschrauber</h2>\n                <p class=\"bba bba--small\" th:text=\"${sku}\">Bestellnummer 0.611.909.000</p>\n                <!-- Bwertungen Platzhalter. so sollten die Bewertungen aussehen. Bazaarvoice? -->\n                <a href=\"#m-rating1\" title=\"\" class=\"m-rating__stars js-scroll-to\" aria-label=\"Product ratings\">\n                  <span class=\"total-ratings\">47 Bewertungen</span>\n                  <input type=\"radio\" name=\"rating\" value=\"5\" id=\"5\">\n                  <label for=\"5\">&#9734;</label>\n                  <input type=\"radio\" name=\"rating\" value=\"4\" id=\"4\">\n                  <label for=\"4\" class=\"checked\">&#9734;</label>\n                  <input type=\"radio\" name=\"rating\" value=\"3\" id=\"3\">\n                  <label for=\"3\" class=\"checked\">&#9734;</label>\n                  <input type=\"radio\" name=\"rating\" value=\"2\" id=\"2\">\n                  <label for=\"2\" class=\"checked\">&#9734;</label>\n                  <input type=\"radio\" name=\"rating\" value=\"1\" id=\"1\">\n                  <label for=\"1\" class=\"checked\">&#9734;</label>\n                  <span class=\"overall-rating\">4.8</span>\n                </a>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"o-gt-stage__info-icons column\">\n\n                <div class=\"o-gt-stage__icons\">\n                  <div class=\"o-gt-stage__icon\">\n                    <picture>\n                      <source srcset=\"_res/img/dummys/bosch_bl_icon_professional_18v_system.png\">\n                      <img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"_res/img/dummys/bosch_bl_icon_professional_18v_system.png\" alt=\"no_dust\">\n                    </picture>\n                  </div>\n\n                  <div class=\"o-gt-stage__icon\">\n                    <picture>\n                      <source srcset=\"_res/img/dummys/bosch_bl_icon_professional_18v_system.png\">\n                      <img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"_res/img/dummys/bosch_bl_icon_professional_18v_system.png\" alt=\"no_dust\">\n                    </picture>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n\n                <p class=\"icons-text bba bba--medium bba--fw-bold\" th:aria-level=\"4\" th:role=\"heading\"\n                   $skuAttr(EXPERT_BENEFIT_DESCRIPTION)$.getText()>Test Bis zu 4x mehr Leistung als der GSR 18V-45 Professional<sup>1</sup></p>\n\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"o-gt-stage__info\">\n                <ul>\n                  <li class=\"bba bba--medium\">Sehr hoher Anwenderschutz dank KickBack Control (ein- und ausschaltbar)</li>\n                  <li class=\"bba bba--medium\">Kraftvoller Motor liefert mit 64 Nm optimale Leistung für anspruchsvolle Anwendungen</li>\n                  <li class=\"bba bba--medium\">Beste Handlichkeit durch kompakte Kopflänge</li>\n                  <li class=\"bba bba--medium\">Volle Kontrolle dank verstellbarer Präzisions-Kupplung</li>\n                </ul>\n                <a href=\"#\" class=\"link o-gt-stage__info__toggle-btn\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"\n                   data-show-more=\"View more\"\n                   data-show-less=\"View less\"\n                   data-aria-show-more=\"View more bullet points\"\n                   data-aria-show-less=\"View less bullet points\">\n                  View more\n                </a>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"o-gt-stage__materials swiper\">\n\n                <div class=\"o-gt-stage__pics-wrapper swiper-wrapper \">\n\n                  <div class=\"pics-tooltip  swiper-slide\" data-title=\"Pic 1 Akkuschrauber 3000\">\n                    <p class=\"pics-tooltip__imgTitle\"><strong>Lochsägen</strong></p>\n                    <div class=\"o-gt-stage__pic duo\">\n                      <picture>\n                        <source srcset=\"_res/img/dummys/m-product_teaser/gsr-12v-15-0601868101_166x164.webp\" type=\"image/webp\">\n                        <img src=\"_res/img/dummys/m-product_teaser/gsr-12v-15-0601868101_166x164.png\" alt=\"alt_Pic 1 Akkuschrauber 3000\">\n                      </picture>\n                      <picture>\n                        <source srcset=\"_res/img/dummys/empty_dummy/125x125.webp\" type=\"image/webp\">\n                        <img src=\"_res/img/dummys/empty_dummy/125x125.png\" alt=\"alt_pic-1-1\">\n                      </picture>\n                    </div>\n                    <p>ø max <strong>68 mm</strong></p>\n                  </div>\n\n                  <div class=\"pics-tooltip pair__1 swiper-slide\" data-title=\"Pic 2\">\n                    <p class=\"pics-tooltip__imgTitle\"><strong>Bohren</strong></p>\n                    <div class=\"o-gt-stage__pic duo\">\n                      <picture>\n                        <source srcset=\"_res/img/dummys/m-product_teaser/gsr-12v-15-0601868101_166x164.webp\" type=\"image/webp\">\n                        <img src=\"_res/img/dummys/m-product_teaser/gsr-12v-15-0601868101_166x164.png\" alt=\"alt_Pic 2\">\n                      </picture>\n                      <picture>\n                        <source srcset=\"_res/img/dummys/empty_dummy/125x125.webp\" type=\"image/webp\">\n                        <img src=\"_res/img/dummys/empty_dummy/125x125.png\" alt=\"alt_pic-1-2\">\n                      </picture>\n                    </div>\n                    <p>ø max <strong>150 mm</strong></p>\n                  </div>\n\n                  <div class=\"pics-tooltip pair__2 swiper-slide\" data-title=\"Pic 3\">\n                    <div class=\"o-gt-stage__pic duo\">\n                      <picture>\n                        <source srcset=\"_res/img/dummys/m-product_teaser/gsr-12v-15-0601868101_166x164.webp\" type=\"image/webp\">\n                        <img src=\"_res/img/dummys/m-product_teaser/gsr-12v-15-0601868101_166x164.png\" alt=\"alt_Pic 3\">\n                      </picture>\n                      <picture>\n                        <source srcset=\"_res/img/dummys/empty_dummy/125x125.webp\" type=\"image/webp\">\n                        <img src=\"_res/img/dummys/empty_dummy/125x125.png\" alt=\"alt_A particularly long text to test how the popup behaves with a lot of text\">\n                      </picture>\n                    </div>\n                    <p>ø max <strong>16 mm</strong></p>\n                  </div>\n\n                  <div class=\"pics-tooltip  swiper-slide\" data-title=\"Pic 4\">\n                    <p class=\"pics-tooltip__imgTitle\"><strong>Schrauben</strong></p>\n                    <div class=\"o-gt-stage__pic \">\n                      <picture>\n                        <source srcset=\"_res/img/dummys/m-product_teaser/gsr-12v-15-0601868101_166x164.webp\" type=\"image/webp\">\n                        <img src=\"_res/img/dummys/m-product_teaser/gsr-12v-15-0601868101_166x164.png\" alt=\"alt_Pic 4\">\n                      </picture>\n                    </div>\n                    <p>ø max <strong>13 mm</strong></p>\n                  </div>\n\n                </div>\n\n                <p class=\"o-gt-stage__materials-subHeadline\"><sup>1</sup>&nbsp;Interner Test unter typischen Arbeitsbedingungen.</p>\n\n              </div>\n\n              <div class=\"o-gt-stage__gallery\">\n                <div class=\"o-gt-stage__modal\" role=\"dialog\" aria-modal=\"false\">\n                  <div class=\"o-gt-stage__modal-close\">\n                    <button type=\"button\" aria-label=\"Close dialog\">\n                      <i class=\"icon-Bosch-Ic-close-black\"></i>\n                    </button>\n                  </div>\n                  <div class=\"swiper swiper-main\" tabindex=\"0\">\n                    <div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n\n                      <div class=\"swiper-slide\" th:each=\"mediaItem, iterStat : ${stageGallery}\">\n                        <div class=\"img-wrapper\">\n                          <picture>\n                            <source srcset=$skuAttr(PRODIMG)$.getImgUrl() th:data-srcset=\"''\" th:srcset=\"$skuAttr(PRODIMG)$.getImgUrl()\" />\n                            <img alt=\"\" class=\"img-responsive lazyload\"\n                                 src=\"_res/img/dummys/gsb18v-1330c_8ah_core_dyn_rna_v2.webp\"\n                                 th:class=\"'img-responsive'\"\n                                 th:data-src=\"$skuAttr(PRODIMG)$.getImgUrl()\"\n                                 th:src=\"$skuAttr(PRODIMG)$.getImgUrl()\" />\n                          </picture>\n                        </div>\n                      </div>\n\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"arrows-desktop\">\n                      <div class=\"swiper-button-next\" role=\"button\" aria-label=\"Swipe to the next slide\"></div>\n                      <div class=\"swiper-button-prev\" role=\"button\" aria-label=\"Swipe to the previous slide\"></div>\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n                  <div class=\"swiper thumbs\">\n                    <div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n\n                      <button type=\"button\" class=\"thumb swiper-slide \">\n                        <picture>\n                          <source media=\"(min-width: 992px)\" data-srcset=\"_res/img/dummys/gsb18v-1330c_8ah_core_dyn_rna_v2.webp\" type=\"image/webp\">\n                          <img data-src=\"_res/img/dummys/gsb18v-1330c_8ah_core_dyn_rna_v2.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"\" height=\"\" class=\"img-responsive lazyload\">\n                        </picture>\n                      </button>\n\n                      <button type=\"button\" class=\"thumb swiper-slide \">\n                        <picture>\n                          <source media=\"(min-width: 992px)\" data-srcset=\"_res/img/dummys/m123-product-table-3.webp\" type=\"image/webp\">\n                          <img data-src=\"_res/img/dummys/m123-product-table-3.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"\" height=\"\" class=\"img-responsive lazyload\">\n                        </picture>\n                      </button>\n\n                      <button type=\"button\" class=\"thumb swiper-slide \">\n                        <picture>\n                          <source media=\"(min-width: 992px)\" data-srcset=\"_res/img/dummys/m350-teaser_boxes.webp\" type=\"image/webp\">\n                          <img data-src=\"_res/img/dummys/m350-teaser_boxes.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"\" height=\"\" class=\"img-responsive lazyload\">\n                        </picture>\n                      </button>\n\n                      <button type=\"button\" class=\"thumb swiper-slide \">\n                        <picture>\n                          <source media=\"(min-width: 992px)\" data-srcset=\"_res/img/dummys/O-06-C-Hotspots_Zoom-product.webp\" type=\"image/webp\">\n                          <img data-src=\"_res/img/dummys/O-06-C-Hotspots_Zoom-product.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"\" height=\"\" class=\"img-responsive lazyload\">\n                        </picture>\n                      </button>\n\n                      <button type=\"button\" class=\"thumb swiper-slide swiper-thumb--cliplister\">\n                        <picture>\n                          <source media=\"(min-width: 992px)\" data-srcset=\"_res/img/dummys/testimg_991px.webp\" type=\"image/webp\">\n                          <img data-src=\"_res/img/dummys/testimg_991px.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"\" height=\"\" class=\"img-responsive lazyload\">\n                        </picture>\n                        <div class=\"video-icon\"></div>\n                      </button>\n\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"swiper-pagination\"></div>\n\n                    <div class=\"swiper-button-next\" role=\"button\" aria-label=\"Swipe to the next slide\"></div>\n                    <div class=\"swiper-button-prev\" role=\"button\" aria-label=\"Swipe to the previous slide\"></div>\n                  </div>\n\n                </div>\n              </div>\n\n              <div class=\"o-gt-stage__icons-wrapper\">\n                <div class=\"o-gt-stage__icons\">\n                  <div class=\"o-gt-stage__icon\">\n                    <picture>\n                      <source srcset=\"_res/img/dummys/bosch_bl_icon_professional_18v_system.png\">\n                      <img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"_res/img/dummys/bosch_bl_icon_professional_18v_system.png\" alt=\"no_dust\">\n                    </picture>\n                  </div>\n\n                  <div class=\"o-gt-stage__icon\">\n                    <picture>\n                      <source srcset=\"_res/img/dummys/Ampshare-logo.png\">\n                      <img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"_res/img/dummys/Ampshare-logo.png\" alt=\"ampshare\">\n                    </picture>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n\n              <div class=\"o-gt-stage__overview\">\n                <div class=\"o-gt-stage__discount\">\n                  <div>\n                    <i class=\"icon-alert-info\"></i>\n                  </div>\n                  <div>\n                    <p class=\"lg\">\n                      Products classified as Warehouse Outlet goods are offered at a special price due to packaging damage. The packaging may have significant scratches, dents, and/or scuff marks. These unopened products are unused, tested, and fully functional, with the original seal intact and the scope of delivery complete.\n                    </p>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n\n                <!-- Exclude Variant Select for AC -->\n\n                <div class=\"o-gt-stage__variant\">\n                  <div class=\"a-select a-select--gray\">\n                    <label class=\"a-select--label-inside\" for=\"select-2\">Variante auswaehlen</label>\n                    <div class=\"a-select__container\">\n                      <select id=\"gt-stage-variant-select\" name=\"gt-stage-variant-select\">\n                        <option value=\"\" disabled>Please select</option>\n                        <option value=\"#1\" data-href=\"#1\">Einzelgeraet</option>\n                        <option value=\"#2\" data-href=\"#2\">mit ProCORE 18V 8.0Ah Akku</option>\n                        <option value=\"#3\" data-href=\"#3\">in L-BOXX 136</option>\n                      </select>\n                      <i class=\"icon-Bosch-Ic-arrow-link-bottom\"></i>\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n\n                <div class=\"o-gt-stage__price\">\n                  <div class=\"in-stock\">\n                    <div>\n                      <div>\n                        <i class=\"icon-denied\"></i>\n                        <p class=\"bba bba--small\">\n                          No returns allowed\n                        </p>\n                      </div>\n                      <div>\n                        <p class=\"bba bba--small\">\n                          Lieferzeit 1-3 Werktage\n                        </p>\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n                  <div class=\"a-pt-price\">\n                    <span class=\"a-pt-price__rrp\">\n                    <div class=\"a-pt-price__flagPlusIcon --transparent crossedPrice\">\n                      <i class=\"icon-user\"></i>\n                      <span class=\"a-pt-price__flag\">-9%</span>\n                    </div>\n                    <span class=\"a-pt-price__flag\">-20%</span>\n                    <span class=\"a-pt-price__text\"></span>\n                      <span class=\"a-pt-price__price\">133.00 EUR</span>\n                      <span class=\"a-pt-price__info\">\n                          <object>\n                            <a href=\"#\" tabindex=\"0\" class=\"a-pt-price__popover\" role=\"button\" data-toggle=\"popover\" data-placement=\"auto\" data-trigger=\"focus\" data-container=\"body\" title=\"\" data-content=\"Lowest total price of the last 30 days before the discount.\" data-original-title=\"Price information\">\n                              <i class=\"icon-alert-info\"></i>\n                            </a>\n                          </object>\n                      </span>\n                    </span>\n                    <span class=\"a-pt-price__current\">\n                    <span class=\"a-pt-price__label\">from</span>\n                    <div class=\"a-pt-price__priceWrapper\">\n                      <span class=\"a-pt-price__price \">372,47 EUR</span>\n                        <span class=\"a-pt-price__gray\">\n                            <span class=\"a-pt-price__label\">inkl. MwSt</span>\n                        </span>\n                    </div>\n                  </span>\n                    <span class=\"a-pt-price__vat\">313,00 EUR exkl. MwSt</span>\n                    <div class=\"a-pt-price__legal-disclaimer\">\n                      <span class=\"legal-disclaimer\">Our prices include VAT, Bebat, Recupel and other taxes and contributions.</span>\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n\n                <div class=\"o-gt-stage__repair-icon\">\n                  <a href=\"#\" class=\"repair-icon-link\" aria-label=\"Check repairability\">\n                    <picture>\n                      <source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"_res/img/dummys/gt-icons/durability.webp\">\n                      <img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"_res/img/dummys/gt-icons/durability.png\" alt=\"Durability\">\n                    </picture>\n                  </a>\n                </div>\n\n                <div class=\"o-gt-stage__cta\">\n                  <button class=\"bba-btn bba-btn--primary bba-btn--md addToCart\">\n                    <i class=\"icon-Bosch-Ic-add-to-cart-black\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i>\n                    In Warenkorb legen\n                  </button>\n\n                  <button class=\"bba-btn bba-btn--secondary bba-btn--md\">\n                    Bei Bosch Partnern kaufen\n                  </button>\n                </div>\n                <script id=\"gtin-3165140889810\"></script>\n                <div class=\"o-gt-stage__payment\">\n                  <span class=\"payment-text\">Payment options</span>\n                  <div class=\"payment-icons-wrapper\">\n                    <img src=\"_res/img/brand/Bosch-Ic-creditcard-mcard.svg\" alt=\"Mastercard\">\n                    <img src=\"_res/img/brand/Bosch-Ic-creditcard-visa.svg\" alt=\"Visa\">\n                    <img src=\"_res/img/brand/Bosch-Ic-creditcard-dinersclub.svg\" alt=\"Dinersclub\">\n                    <img src=\"_res/img/brand/Bosch-Ic-creditcard-amex.svg\" alt=\"Amex\">\n                    <img src=\"_res/img/brand/Bosch-Ic-creditcard-maestrocard.svg\" alt=\"Maestro\">\n                    <img src=\"_res/img/brand/Paypal.svg\" alt=\"Paypal\">\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <!-- END: Component Markup -->\n  </div>\n\n<script>\n  var CONF = {\n    ASSET_PATH: 'https://www.bosch-professional.com/res/',\n    ENV: 'development', // production\n    DEALER_ONLINE_API: 'https://rvw-boschpt.kittelberger.net/de/de/dealers3-rvw/retailers/online',\n    DEALER_OFFLINE_API: 'https://rvw-boschpt.kittelberger.net/de/de/dealers3-rvw/retailers/offline',\n    BITURBO_BACKOFFICE_TABLE: 'https://rvw-boschpt.kittelberger.net/gb/en/biturbo-register/backoffice'\n  }\n</script>\n\n<!-- Include the latest & greatest cliplister plugin -->\n<script src=\"https://mycliplister.com/merge?cliplister=1.12&clviewer=1.44&videostage=1.29&innercontrols=1.14&clickablevideo=1.6&playbutton=1.2&previewimage=1.7&bufferingspinner=1.6\"></script>\n\n<script src=\"https://www.bosch-professional.com/res/main.bundle.js\"></script>\n\n</body>\n\n</html>\n",
  "labels": {
    "eshop.exclusive": "",
    "eshop.product.refurbished.pricing.long": "Wiederaufbereitete Produkte sind preisg\\u00FCnstiger als das entsprechende Neuprodukt im Bosch Professional Power Tools Online Shop Wiederaufbereitete Produkte k\\u00F6nnen verkratzt und gebraucht sein. Das Produkt befindet sich m\\u00F6glicherweise nicht in der Originalverpackung und das Verpackungssiegel ist ge\\u00F6ffnet. M\\u00F6glicherweise fehlt Aktionszubeh\\u00F6r. Wiederaufbereitete Produkte sind vollst\\u00E4ndig getestet und werden mit Anleitungen ausgeliefert. Wiederaufbereitete Produkte haben bei Vorlage des Orignalkaufbelegs eine Garantie von 12 Monaten (die Garantie kann durch eine Online-Registrierung nicht verl\\u00E4ngert werden). Alle weiteren Lieferbedingungen entsprechen denen des jeweiligen Neuprodukts.",
    "eshop.product.warehouse.pricing.long": "Lagerprodukte sind preisg\\u00FCnstiger als das entsprechende Neuprodukt im Bosch Professional Power Tools Online Shop. Ein Lagerprodukt ist nicht gebraucht, allerdings kann die Originalverpackung besch\\u00E4digt (z. B. angeschlagen oder verkratzt) sein. Alternativ wird das Produkt m\\u00F6glicherweise in einem braunen neutralen Karton geliefert. Lagerprodukte beinhalten das gleiche Zubeh\\u00F6r, die gleichen Dokumente und Anleitungen sowie die gleichen Garantiebedingungen wie das entsprechende Neuprodukt. Die Lieferbedingungen entsprechen denen des jeweiligen Neuprodukts.",
